Executive Profile
Richard S. Strong  Chief Executive Officer, Strong Investments IncAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.76--
Background

		Mr. Richard S. Strong is the Managing Partner at Calm Waters Partnership. Previously, he was the Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at Strong Capital Management, Inc. Mr. Strong was also a Security Analyst and Portfolio Manager at Strong Capital Management, Inc. He has been in the investment management business since 1967. Mr. Strong was the Chairman of Strong Financial Corporation and Strong Mutual Funds.	
	



